    infrastructure for that client's internal use;
  - forks and modifications used internally;
  - non-commercial research, education, and personal projects;
  - distribution to clients alongside professional services, provided
    clients receive the Software under this same License.

4. CONTRIBUTIONS

The project accepts contributions only under the Contributor License Agreement
